      <title>韩国总统在投票前任命新的政策职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-korea-president-forms-new-post-for-policy-ahead-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈设立了一个新的政策职位，并更换了所有五名高级秘书，就在几个月前举行的选举中，他的政党正试图重新获得议会的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/south-korea-president-forms-new-post-for-policy-ahead-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联社报道，缅甸军队在民兵协同袭击中节节败退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-01/myanmar-s-military-is-losing-ground-against-coordinated-nationwide-attacks-buoying-opposition-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷（美联社）——由三支装备精良的少数民族民兵组成的联盟对缅甸军政府发动了大约两周的大规模攻势，一名陆军上尉在靠近中国东北边境的丛林地区作战，他感叹自己从未见过这样的战斗。激烈的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-01/myanmar-s-military-is-losing-ground-against-coordinated-nationwide-attacks-buoying-opposition-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 01:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
